<br>
I have a level 56 Wood Elf Warrior that needs some upgrades. I'm living with a rather limited budget at the moment but have ways to get money.<br>
<br>
Take a look at my profile and tell me anywhere that I can upgrade...<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=313342">Yraen</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
Also, I'm the <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Main Tank</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> for a mid-sized guild that doesn't have much power behind it right now. Therefore I need all the HP's, AC, and Taunt I can get... <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><br>
<!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=107814"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Waeolwen Lightpath</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Druid of 56 Circles<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=313342"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Yraen</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Warrior of 56 Circles<br>
Member of <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.crys.org/cof/cof.htm"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Circle of Faith</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=waeolwenthedruid>WaeolwenTheDruid</A> at: 12/4/02 9:23:34 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pertietrull>PertieTrull</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/4/02 11:50:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4558.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_sword.gif" align=absmiddle>  re:</span><hr size=1> well, you didn't say what your guild is capable of, and how much plat you can anticipate having available to you to upgrade.<br>
<br>
Getting your epic would be a  big help for you, a Willsapper would be probably the best weapon that you are capable of.<br>
<br>
Are you able to get into HOT to get some myrmidon armor? that would be the easiest and cheapest way for you to upgrade. <br>
<br>
You can go for an eyepatch of plunder for face, shaderock amulet from vah dynn for neck. Draconic paldrons are an easy upgrade, and bracers of benevolence while you are in WW. Solstice earring is a nice buyable upgrade for your ear slot and only runs about 7k for the parts. Look into a lodi belt, I assume that your guild can drop lodi. If your guild can help with these things, look at picking up a dragon haste item.<br>
<br>
You might also be able to do the chardok ring/cord quests, strength of the elements, and the thurg rings. These would all be huge upgrades for you, and will give you some nice goals.<br>
<br>
All of these should be achievable for a lower/mid range guild if the members are similar level to you. This gives you some questing to do on your own as well.  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pertietrull>PertieTrull</A> at: 12/4/02 11:52:34 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=waeolwenthedruid>WaeolwenTheDruid</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/02 6:26:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4558.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_sword.gif" align=absmiddle>  Equipment Suggestions...</span><hr size=1> Oh yea... the guild that I am in is mostly about my level and a little lower. But, a lot of my RL friends are in a higher level guild that does HoT a lot (along with other places around and above that level.) and I'm kinda an honorary member of the guild. Until I join it, at least. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
