</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=waeolwenthedruid>WaeolwenTheDruid</A> at: 12/5/02 6:29:54 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=nissav>Nissa V</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 35<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/02 6:44:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4558.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_sword.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Equipment Suggestions...</span><hr size=1> Id look at yer weapons possibly.  Not sure that the procs on those are high taunt.<br>
<br>
But not to bad for a low to mid guild character. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=414380"><br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.centurytel.net/Aikido1/Nissa2.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kiyallmanebloodcry>KiyallmaneBloodcry</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>/cons RED</span><br>  Posts: 337<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/02 10:35:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4558.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~bass72/_uimages/1C.gif hieght=140 width=113></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_sword.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Equipment Suggestions...</span><hr size=1> I'd suggest a Frostbringer, I've been quite happy with mine.  I'd also, if your guild has the strength, spend lots of time in Kael Arena or the Plate house and do the cycle.  You may want to take a look at the Full Mithril (advanced high elf cultural) armor for some slots, especially bracers, good ac and resists for MT.  That, or a pair of Bracers of Benevolence.  <p><b><i><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=75761>Kiyallmane Bloodcry</a></i></b><br>
Fier'Dal Warlord<br>
and her faithful sidekick,<br> <b><i><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=159663>Gameon Dal`Kambur</a></i></b><br>
Proud officer of <b><i><a href=http://www.destinysflame.com>Destiny's Flame</a></i></b><br>
Torvonnilous<br>
<i>"These Memories Never Sleep...."</i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=shadokastr>shadokastr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 43<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/5/02 3:01:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4558.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_sword.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Equipment Suggestions...</span><hr size=1> my first suggestion is lose those weaps hehe.  i have used both and neither are very desirable for aggro.  Both sell for quite a bit on my server (karana), i would say sell both the spiked malled and snowchipper and try for wavecrasher and frosty.  Should be about an even trade.  as for the gear<br>
<br>
helm:raldukan, cobalt or champ<br>
face:crystal spider eyes<br>
boots:cobalt, champs or cultural<br>
arms:cobalt, champs or cultural<br>
<br>
***after that its all about haste, shoot for RBG or better, haste goes a long ways.<br>
<br>
looks pretty ok all in all.  Enlist your guilds help, the better equiped you are and higher level you are the more they can take down.  Levels &gt; Weps &gt; Gear.<br>
<br>
 <p>Nevian Shadowforge<br>
55th Myrmidon of Karana<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=146119">www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=146119</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
